{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"绿草湖（外一首）","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":3}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿草湖（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见天鹅对我说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠里有一座天国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名字就叫“绿草湖”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸上长满了青草。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草丛里有一只白兔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一个奴隶来引道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受难者和他的爱人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逃到这里落户了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，天鹅，那是天国吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里可有金翅鸟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，天鹅，那是乐园吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里可有绿葡萄？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那黑暗的年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆仑山也被锁着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说这“世外桃源”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是大监狱的一角？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看沙海把天幕揭开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵驼铃传来；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社吹起了铜号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖里飞出金翅鸟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的绿草湖呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是沙海中的宝岛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天鹅对着牧人唱啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧人骑上天鹅飞哟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1961年10月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记于塔克拉玛干沙海的边缘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯尔克孜族的少女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从戈壁滩上走过——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手上牵着一只羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩上扛着坎土镘（注），"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫红的披巾似榴花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪白的裙衣闪成河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你对东不拉这样说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“坎土镘就是花朵。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东不拉给你编一首歌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你是一只白天鹅。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）坎土镘是新疆各兄弟民族使用的一种农具，类似锄头，锄面很大，扁圆。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}